data.description: Discover the potential of 309 Sandlewood Drive, a classic 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home with a traditional layout.  This townhome offers a unique opportunity to revitalize and personalize a timeless design. The cozy living area is complete with a wood burning fireplace. The bedrooms are spacious and practically laid out to provide the ideal foundation for your creative vision. With a little TLC, this property can be transformed into a welcoming haven that reflects your unique style. The spacious backyard adds to the possibilities. Located conveniently near Summerville's amenities, this home is a prime candidate for your investment and renovation expertise. Don't miss out on this chance to make 309 Sandlewood Drive your own.
